Class InputConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • proteomicsdb.org.requesttool.model.description.InputConfiguration
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    InputConfigurationChangeable, InputConfigurationValidated

    public abstract class InputConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
    This class stores the values the user has specified for the input parameters of the API, and the information which output columns he has selected. It belongs to exactly one API.
